{"tid":2373232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林嘉泰昏迷｜投身社署工作33年 多次陪林鄭落區上鏡率甚高","createTime":"2021-01-20T09:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T10:45:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"98b76dabb3e20a31a57fef4a5db3684be9e7464b","tid":2373232,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/33-0FGgcf4vU1SnvtXPELgItOcA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7NSIDB3FBNHOVD7GWKKPLJIBUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F33-0FGgcf4vU1SnvtXPELgItOcA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7NSIDB3FBNHOVD7GWKKPLJIBUE.jpg&h=71b4e635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會福利署副署長林嘉泰，今日突然在灣仔胡忠大廈辦公室內昏迷。資料顯示，林嘉泰於1987年7月加入社署工作，2013年9月升任副署長（服務），目前因署長梁松泰放大假，暫代署長一職。特首林鄭月娥過去曾任社會福利署長，翻查政府新聞處報道，即使林鄭日後官至發展局局長、政務司司長甚至特首之位，林嘉泰仍不時跟隨林鄭落區，另外亦會跟隨其他官員外訪及見記者，上鏡率甚高。<br />\n<br />\n2011年2月4日，林鄭時任發展局長，當日在林嘉泰陪同下，前往黃大仙及香港仔探望獨居老人，當時林嘉泰是社署助理署長（津貼）；2012年6月林嘉泰曾跟隨時任社署署長的聶德權前往上海考察。聶德權為林鄭愛將，現時他已官至公務員事務局局長；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210120/GBP56CMA2VEH3PLMMYDN3ZWTWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210120%2FGBP56CMA2VEH3PLMMYDN3ZWTWA%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=05f850e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210120%2FGBP56CMA2VEH3PLMMYDN3ZWTWA%2F&h=9c9feba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210120/GBP56CMA2VEH3PLMMYDN3ZWTWA/</a>"},{"pid":"b5e5c20dde1f5c564ad7f9ec07e036081abfd0e8","tid":2373232,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"幾時死"},{"pid":"0c4d8c54f2d7189ff40efbc401c3972e69baf5a2","tid":2373232,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dis